<h1 class='text-white' 
    style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 46px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: capitalize; margin-bottom: 20px;">
  👋 Welcome.
</h1>

<p class="lead" 
   style="color: #f0f0f0; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 700px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
  💡 Software development is not a secret process. When I take on a new project, my goal is not only to deliver a <strong>well-crafted product</strong> but also to ensure that each stage of the process is fully communicated and transparent.
</p>

<p class="lead">
  <%= link_to "🚀 About Me", about_path, 
      class: "btn btn-lg fw-bold", 
      style: "background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb, #2575fc); 
              color: white; 
              border: none; 
              border-radius: 50px; 
              padding: 14px 34px; 
              font-size: 18px; 
              text-decoration: none; 
              box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); 
              transition: all 0.3s ease;" %>
</p>

<style>
  .btn:hover {
    transform: scale(1.08);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2575fc, #6a11cb);
  }
</style>
